' Figure 7 - Lease Management Process (State Diagram)

[*] --> Draft

Draft --> Active : approve & sign
Draft --> Cancelled : cancel

Active --> Renewed : renew
Active --> Terminated : terminate
Active --> Expired : end_date reached

Renewed --> Active : process renewal

Expired --> [*]
Terminated --> [*]
Cancelled --> [*]

note right of Draft
  Lease created but not yet active
  Awaiting approval and signatures
end note

note right of Active
  Tenant occupying unit
  Payments being tracked
  Normal operations
end note

note right of Expired
  Lease term completed normally
  Unit becomes available
end note

note right of Terminated
  Early termination by either party
  May involve penalties
end note

note right of Renewed
  Existing lease extended
  New terms may apply
end note

@enduml
